    <h3>Software Developer</h3>
    <p class="instructions">
      Based in Montevideo, Uruguay, I have 9+ years of experience working with
      Python/Django and similar backend technologies. I recently rediscovered
      the beauty of frontend development and started my journey with React,
      NextJS and Astro. Take a look around ðŸ‘‰ to know more about my experience,
